Package: badgerdrop
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: BadgerDrop Team <badgerdrop@example.com>
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11),
         python3-gi,
         gir1.2-gtk-4.0,
         gir1.2-adw-1,
         libgirepository-1.0-1,
         desktop-file-utils,
         shared-mime-info
Description: macOS-style AppImage installer for Linux
 BadgerDrop provides a macOS-style drag-and-drop installation experience
 for AppImage files on Linux. It features a clean GTK4 interface,
 sound notifications, and easy management of installed applications.
